You can't just barge in on the tour

39:29.286 --> 39:30.579
without purchasing a ticket.

39:31.747 --> 39:33.498
You're giving us a tour for free.

39:34.082 --> 39:35.209
For free. Of course.

39:36.001 --> 39:37.586
The Code Noir,

39:37.669 --> 39:40.797
a decree that dictated
the conditions of slavery,

39:40.881 --> 39:42.758
did not exist on these grounds.

39:42.841 --> 39:45.886
It was replaced
by the Madame's own code of terror.

39:45.969 --> 39:48.889
And the torture
she inflicted on her slaves would spawn

39:48.972 --> 39:52.392
179 years of hauntings.

39:52.476 --> 39:55.229
Wasn't this house
owned by the guy in <i>Face/Off?</i>

39:55.312 --> 39:58.357
FEMALE TOUR GUIDE: Correct, the actor
Nicolas Cage was a previous owner.

39:58.440 --> 40:00.984
Madame LaLaurie
was infamous for her vanity.

40:01.068 --> 40:03.987
She fought the rigors of age
with a sacrament

40:04.071 --> 40:05.781
<i>of expensive creams from Europe</i>

40:06.490 --> 40:08.408
<i>and something else</i>
<i>far more exotic.</i>

40:08.867 --> 40:10.702
DELPHINE: Oh, I'm running out.

40:11.537 --> 40:12.829
We gonna have to get some more.

40:12.913 --> 40:14.748
No! Please don't make me.

40:14.831 --> 40:16.416
You think I want to do this?

40:17.000 --> 40:19.461
You can blame your father
and his fresh-faced whore.

40:19.545 --> 40:21.463
Unless you'd like
to split your inheritance

40:21.547 --> 40:23.966
with an endless parade
of colored bastards.

40:26.093 --> 40:27.553
(CHAINS CLANGING)

40:29.555 --> 40:30.848
(SCREAMING)

40:35.811 --> 40:37.312
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

40:38.146 --> 40:39.147
(SPEAKS SOFTLY)

40:42.860 --> 40:45.946
FEMALE TOUR GUIDE: <i>The secret ingredient</i>
<i>to the Madame's beauty ritual</i>

40:46.029 --> 40:49.241
<i>was a poultice</i>
<i>made from human pancreas.</i>

40:49.324 --> 40:52.411
This is the infamous chamber of horrors.

40:52.953 --> 40:54.580
No flash photography, please.

40:54.955 --> 40:59.585
The attic where Madame LaLaurie
inflicted heinous torture

40:59.668 --> 41:00.961
upon her slaves.

41:01.044 --> 41:04.590
And where she ultimately met
her own demise.

41:17.019 --> 41:18.312
(SPEAKING OTHER LANGUAGE)

41:18.395 --> 41:19.688
Get off my property!

41:19.897 --> 41:22.524
I've heard that
you are in need of my services.

41:22.608 --> 41:23.984
What could a Negress have
that I would ever want?

41:24.651 --> 41:26.570
<i>Mon pele,</i> Marie Laveau.

41:26.778 --> 41:29.323
I have the cure
for your husband's affliction.

41:29.406 --> 41:32.075
His compulsion for young ladies.

41:32.159 --> 41:34.286
I'll have you flogged
for your insolence!

41:34.411 --> 41:35.621
A love potion

41:37.039 --> 41:38.999
to ensure fidelity.

41:43.545 --> 41:46.131
If the potion entrances
as you promise,

41:46.215 --> 41:47.883
your future's assured.

41:47.966 --> 41:50.302
To our future together.

41:50.802 --> 41:52.054
<i>Salud.</i>

41:54.556 --> 41:55.933
Mmm.

41:56.475 --> 41:58.185
It's like honeysuckle.

42:04.566 --> 42:06.360
Oh.

42:06.568 --> 42:08.028
Ooh.

42:09.196 --> 42:10.697
Oh.

42:12.950 --> 42:14.785
Ooh, yes.

42:14.868 --> 42:16.161
(CLEARS THROAT)

42:16.662 --> 42:18.038
Oh, no.

42:18.121 --> 42:19.373
Oh, God!

42:19.915 --> 42:21.083
What did...

42:21.166 --> 42:22.626
(MUMBLES)

42:22.709 --> 42:24.670
(GROANING)

42:27.005 --> 42:28.632
(COUGHING) Get it...

42:29.174 --> 42:30.425
Get it out of me.

42:32.636 --> 42:34.221
FEMALE TOUR GUIDE:
<i>Unbeknownst to Madame LaLaurie,</i>

42:34.304 --> 42:37.683
<i>a slave she had brutally mutilated</i>
<i>was Marie Laveau's lover,</i>

42:37.766 --> 42:39.893
<i>and she came to exact her revenge.</i>

42:40.727 --> 42:42.312
(FLOORBOARDS CREAKING)

42:42.396 --> 42:43.772
(MEN COUGHING)

42:52.865 --> 42:56.285
<i>Mo cher,</i>
what has she done to you?

43:02.291 --> 43:03.333
(CRYING)

43:07.921 --> 43:12.384
The potion inflicted its cruel justice,
and she got what she richly deserved.

43:13.010 --> 43:14.553
But her body was never found.

43:14.928 --> 43:18.015
To this day, no one knows
the final resting place

43:18.098 --> 43:19.474
of Madame LaLaurie.

43:26.940 --> 43:28.108
What do you hear?

43:29.943 --> 43:31.612
The lady of the house.

43:56.803 --> 43:58.889
(PEOPLE SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)

44:22.412 --> 44:24.790
(MONITOR BEEPING STEADILY)

44:35.425 --> 44:36.552
Oh, please.

44:36.969 --> 44:38.679
Please let it be him, please.

44:42.766 --> 44:44.351
(ZOE SIGHS)

44:44.643 --> 44:47.020
(MONITOR CONTINUES BEEPING)

44:53.318 --> 44:54.987
It should have been you, asshole.

45:13.839 --> 45:16.508
It's the second door
on your left down the hall.

45:16.592 --> 45:18.343
Make sure you stack 'em vertically.

45:18.427 --> 45:20.012
I'm responsible for those girls.

45:20.095 --> 45:21.680
What if something had happened?

45:21.763 --> 45:23.724
-Well, nothing did.
-Where's Zoe Benson?

45:23.807 --> 45:25.225
How would I know that?

45:25.809 --> 45:26.977
(HORN HONKING)

45:27.060 --> 45:28.770
Oh, that's my taxi.

45:29.188 --> 45:30.397
Here, darling.

45:30.480 --> 45:32.941
Make sure you tip them generously
when they're done.

45:34.109 --> 45:35.402
Where are you going?

45:35.485 --> 45:37.112
Out. Don't wait up.

45:37.196 --> 45:40.324
I have half a mind to enchant the locks
after you leave.

45:40.407 --> 45:43.035
(LAUGHS) Don't make me
drop a house on you.

45:43.118 --> 45:44.161
(DOOR CLOSES)

45:44.244 --> 45:46.121
ZOE: <i>When the levees broke,</i>

45:46.205 --> 45:48.415
<i>the people of New Orleans were tested.</i>

45:48.874 --> 45:51.001
<i>Those who stayed,</i>
<i>stayed for a reason.</i>

45:51.793 --> 45:54.171
<i>With that came a sense</i>
<i>of purpose and community.</i>

45:54.796 --> 45:56.840
<i>That's what happens in a crisis.</i>

45:57.007 --> 46:00.177
<i>All the bullshit falls away, and what's</i>
<i>left is just so raw and vulnerable.</i>

46:00.260 --> 46:01.512
(CRYING)

46:01.595 --> 46:04.515
<i>It's agony to let</i>
<i>people see you so exposed.</i>

46:04.932 --> 46:07.226
<i>It takes a huge amount of trust,</i>

46:07.309 --> 46:10.729
<i>and for most of us,</i>
<i>that trust was shattered long ago.</i>

46:11.313 --> 46:13.398
<i>But, like it or not, we need each other.</i>

46:13.482 --> 46:15.359
<i>And we need each other desperately.</i>

46:16.527 --> 46:17.778
<i>My mother was right.</i>

46:18.445 --> 46:20.614
<i>The world isn't safe for a girl like me.</i>

46:21.615 --> 46:23.742
<i>But maybe I'm not safe</i>
<i>for the world, either.</i>

46:25.452 --> 46:28.497
<i>And since I'll never be able</i>
<i>to experience real love,</i>

46:28.580 --> 46:30.374
<i>might as well put this curse to some use.</i>

46:32.626 --> 46:33.877
(BEEPING)

46:39.842 --> 46:41.260
(RAPID BEEPING)

46:50.435 --> 46:51.687
(MONITOR FLATLINES)

47:01.196 --> 47:02.406
Excellent work, gentlemen.

47:02.489 --> 47:04.491
Just set it down right here.

47:08.036 --> 47:10.622
Well, I'd thank you,

47:11.456 --> 47:15.294
but you're never gonna remember
any of this anyhow.

47:29.892 --> 47:31.143
(MUFFLED GROANING)

47:40.027 --> 47:41.403
(GROANS)

47:42.696 --> 47:43.780
(CHAINS CLINKING)

47:49.786 --> 47:50.871
(HEAVY SIGH)

47:55.375 --> 47:57.085
Come on, Mary Todd Lincoln.

47:58.128 --> 47:59.505
I'll buy you a drink.
